---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 97
  - Title: Theaetetus
    Location: 158 B
By: Plato
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Illusion=The Cosmic Dream
---
How can you determine whether at this moment we are sleeping, and all our
thoughts are a dream; or whether we are awake, and talking to one another in
the waking state?
